  "text": "We thus ran our experiments on three Intel GPUs: HD 520, HD 5500 and Iris 6100. The results were similar across the GPUs, so for conciseness, we report only on the Iris 6100 GPU (driver 20.19.15.4463) with a host CPU i3-5157U. The Iris has a reported 47 compute units. Results for the other Intel GPUs are available in the extended version of this paper [CITATION_1] .",
